{#-
  Telegram MarkdownV2 report layout (spec: notifier-telegram §需求 结构化布局).
  Structure: 抬头(非 intent) → 覆盖行 → 发现(四元组去重 + severity 降序 + 来源)
  → 根因分析 (发现优先). Multi-target findings section by host when
  distinct(non-None target_name) > 1 or fleet; single-host agent degrades to
  flat list. Every dynamic value passes through `mdv2_escape`; `*` / `↳` / `·`
  are structural / literal glyphs the truncation balancer accounts for.
-#}
{{ severity | sev_icon }} *Hostlens 巡检 · {{ report.target_name | mdv2_escape }} · {{ severity | sev_label | mdv2_escape }}*
{% if report.meta %}
{{ report.meta.timestamp | fmt_time | mdv2_escape }} · {{ report.meta.inspectors_used | coverage | mdv2_escape }}
{% endif %}
{% set failed = report.inspector_results | failed_checks %}
{% if failed %}

*失败检查*
{% for target_name, label, inspectors in failed %}
{{ target_name | mdv2_escape }} · {{ label | mdv2_escape }}：{{ inspectors | join("、") | mdv2_escape }}
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}
{% if report.findings %}
{% set sections = report.findings | dedup | group_by_target(fleet=(report.meta is not none and report.meta.target_type == "fleet")) %}

*发现*
{% for target_name, group in sections %}
{% if target_name is not none %}

{{ (group | section_severity) | sev_icon }} *{{ target_name | mdv2_escape }} · {{ (group | section_severity) | sev_label | mdv2_escape }}*
{% elif sections | length > 1 %}

*（未标注主机）*
{% endif %}
{% for f in group | sort_sev %}
{{ f.severity | sev_icon }} {{ f.message | mdv2_escape }} \({{ f.inspector_name | mdv2_escape }}\)
{% endfor %}
{% endfor %}
{% else %}

✅ 未发现异常
{% endif %}
{% if report.hypotheses %}

*根因分析*
{% for h in report.hypotheses %}
• {{ h.description | mdv2_escape }} \(置信度 {{ h.confidence | conf_label | mdv2_escape }}\)
{% for action in h.suggested_actions %}
↳ {{ action | mdv2_escape }}
{% endfor %}
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}
